* Extension of Steno logger designed for use particularly with Steno encoder
 * while also providing log event rate limiting. This class is thread safe.
 *
 * @since 1.12.0
 *
 * @author Ville Koskela (vkoskela at groupon dot com)

* Log for a particular level using the ARRAY_MARKER. * * @param level The log event level. * @param event The log event name. * @param message The log event message. * @param dataKeys The array of data keys. * @param dataValues The array of data values. * @param throwable The Throwable.

* Log for a particular level using the LISTS_MARKER. * * @param level The log event level. * @param event The log event name. * @param dataKeys The List of data keys. * @param dataValues The List of data values. * @param contextKeys The List of context keys. * @param contextValues The List of context values. * @param throwable The Throwable.
